  "text": "Just… it's unimportant, but just roughly how many other of these galaxies has Ra, shall we say, traveled to? I am Ra. We have opened our hearts in radiation of love to the entire creation. Approximately 90 percent of the creation is at some level aware of the sending and able to reply. All of the infinite Logoi are one in the consciousness of love. This is the type of contact which we enjoy rather than travel.",
